						               													<description>Fatal Flaw is a dice-rolling real-time battle game for 2-4 players published by Button Shy Games and sent to Patreon Backers of it's Board Game of the Month Club. It consists of 4 character cards and a PDF of rules page. Player will need to provide up 2 8 dice and 40 tokens or chips in order to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players each select a character and begin rolling their dice, when they think their dice are both higher than another player's they can call Hit, the game is paused and the hit is resolved. There are special rolls for blocks, heals, and special moves for each character. If a player gets 6 hits against them, they have to contend with their fatal flaw and play at a disadvantage. If a player gets 10 hits against them they are out. Last one standing wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
